show_details.name: EDI-Live!
show_details.description:
My show is everything to do with the arts; that means music, film, theatre and much much more! Topics vary from week to week filled with interesting facts, case studies, events happening in Edinburgh and topped off with some of my favourite tracks inbetween! I talk about new trends within the arts, things which interest me and my art. i.e. ideas of nostaliga within film, masculinity within the arts and 'should celebs have political authority?' 
I have experience working for Radio Jackie, a SW London FM radio station assisting producers, presenters and reading the travel/news bulletin so I would like to have my own show to show my skills. I hope you consider me for a show!
The essay should evidence an understanding of what a director does and how the director’s idea is developed for a drama film.
